{
  "texts": [
    "The phantom consists of a soft tissue made of silicon resin mixed with styrofoam beds that simulates the liver, and a cart that moves the liver mimicking respiration.",
    "The cart includes actuators to achieve the desired motion through pneumatic actuation.",
    "The liver phantom moves in two DoF simulating the SI and AP motion.",
    "Additionally, a spherical target made of lead with a diameter of 3 mm was placed inside of the liver phantom.",
    "The liver phantom is shown in Fig. 1 and Fig."
  ]
}